SELECT 
  f1.Series_title_1,
  count(m1.c_tinyint) AS c_tinyint_count,
  count(m1.c_smallint) AS c_small_int_count

FROM Macro_1 AS m1, Filter_1 AS f1

WHERE f1.p_string != NULL

GROUP BY 
  m1.c_boolean, f1.Series_title_1

HAVING c_small_int_count > 0

LIMIT 20
